# Template for tests/Browser PayPal E2E credentials. Committed (no secrets).
#
# Local: copy to `.env.testing` and fill in real SANDBOX values (that file is gitignored).
# CI:    set these as GitHub Actions repository secrets of the same names.
#
# Sandbox REST app:  https://developer.paypal.com/dashboard/applications/sandbox
# On the linked sandbox business account, enable
# "Advanced Credit and Debit Card Payments" so guest card checkout works.

PAYPAL_SANDBOX_CLIENT_ID=
PAYPAL_SANDBOX_CLIENT_SECRET=
